import React from "react";
import {
  StyleSheet,
  Image,
  Text,
  TextInput,
  View,
  ImageBackground,
} from "react-native";

export default function LoginScreen() {
  return (
    <View style={styles.Login}>
      <View style={styles.Group818}>
        <View style={styles.Group335}>
          <Text style={styles.Txt1066}>LOGO</Text>
          <Text style={styles.Txt772}>LOGIN</Text>
          <View style={styles.Group10579}>
            <Text style={styles.phonelabel}>Phone Number</Text>
            <View style={styles.Content}>
              <TextInput
                style={styles.phonenumberfield}
                placeholder="Enter Your Pin"
              />
            </View>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.TextInput}>
            <Text style={styles.Txt498}>Password</Text>
            <View style={styles.Content1}>
              <TextInput
                style={styles.passwordfield}
                placeholder="Enter Your Pin"
              />
              <Image
                style={styles.IconlyLightOutlineHide}
                source={{
                  uri: "https://firebasestorage.googleapis.com/v0/b/unify-bc2ad.appspot.com/o/9hdejqknpam-493%3A920?alt=media&token=9f53b714-e1b5-4a0a-bd07-73aec61ad09e",
                }}
              />
            </View>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.Group5101}>
            <View style={styles.Box} />
            <Text style={styles.rememberme}>Remember me</Text>
            <Text style={styles.forgotpw}>Forgot Password?</Text>
          </View>
          <View style={styles.Button}>
            <Text style={styles.Login}>LOGIN</Text>
          </View>
        </View>
        <Text style={styles.reg}>Dont have an account? Register</Text>
      </View>
    </View>
  );
}

const styles = StyleSheet.create({
  Login: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    justifyContent: "flex-start",
    alignItems: "flex-start",
    paddingTop: 0,
    paddingBottom: 45,
    paddingLeft: 0,
    paddingRight: 0,
    marginLeft: 24,
    marginRight: 24,

    backgroundColor: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)",
    width: 428,
    height: 926,
  },
  Group818: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    alignItems: "center",
  },
  TypeDefaultComponentTopBar: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "row",
    justifyContent: "flex-start",
    alignItems: "center",
    paddingTop: 10,
    paddingBottom: 8,
    paddingLeft: 22,
    paddingRight: 22,
    marginBottom: 15,
  },
  Txt418: {
    fontSize: 16,
    fontFamily: "Urbanist, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "600",
    lineHeight: 22,
    letterSpacing: 0.2,
    color: "rgba(33,33,33,1)",
    marginRight: 283,
  },
  Group: {
    width: 18,
    height: 10,
    marginRight: 5,
  },
  Group1: {
    width: 15.27,
    height: 10.97,
    marginRight: 6,
  },
  Group2: {
    width: 26.98,
    height: 13,
  },

  Group335: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    marginBottom: 334,
  },
  Txt1066: {
    fontSize: 24,
    fontFamily: "Urbanist, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "800",
    letterSpacing: -0.48,
    color: "rgba(253,169,42,1)",
    marginBottom: 93,
  },
  Txt772: {
    fontSize: 32,
    fontFamily: "Urbanist, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "800",
    letterSpacing: -0.64,
    color: "rgba(33,33,33,1)",
    marginBottom: 14,
  },
  Group10579: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    marginBottom: 11,
  },
  phonelabel: {
    fontSize: 14,
    fontFamily: "Urbanist, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "400",
    lineHeight: 24,
    color: "rgba(33,33,33,1)",
    marginBottom: 7,
  },
  Content: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "row",
    justifyContent: "flex-end",
    alignItems: "center",
    paddingTop: 9,
    paddingBottom: 9,
    paddingLeft: 15,
    paddingRight: 15,
    borderRadius: 4,
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderStyle: "solid",
    borderColor: "rgba(253,169,42,1)",
    width: 380,
  },
  phonenumberfield: {
    fontSize: 14,
    fontFamily: "Urbanist, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "400",
    lineHeight: 24,
    color: "rgba(51,51,51,1)",
    width: "80%",
    height: 25,
  },

  TextInput: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    marginBottom: 12,
  },
  Txt498: {
    fontSize: 14,
    fontFamily: "Urbanist, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "400",
    lineHeight: 24,
    color: "rgba(0,0,0,1)",
    marginBottom: 7,
  },
  Content1: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "row",
    justifyContent: "flex-end",
    alignItems: "center",
    paddingTop: 9,
    paddingBottom: 9,
    paddingLeft: 15,
    paddingRight: 15,
    borderRadius: 4,
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderStyle: "solid",
    borderColor: "rgba(208,208,208,1)",
    width: 380,
  },
  passwordfield: {
    fontSize: 14,
    fontFamily: "Urbanist, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "400",
    lineHeight: 24,
    color: "rgba(97,97,97,1)",
    width: 325,
    height: 25,
    marginRight: 8,
    borderWidth: 0,
    borderBottomColor: "white",
    outline: "none",
  },
  IconlyLightOutlineHide: {
    width: 16,
    height: 16,
  },

  Group5101: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "row",
    marginBottom: 49,
  },
  Box: {
    backgroundColor: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)",
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderStyle: "solid",
    borderColor: "rgba(118,118,118,1)",
    width: 16,
    height: 16,
    borderRadius: 2,
    marginRight: 8,
  },
  rememberme: {
    fontSize: 12,
    fontFamily: "Roboto, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "400",
    color: "rgba(87,87,87,1)",
    marginRight: 178,
  },
  forgotpw: {
    fontSize: 12,
    fontFamily: "Roboto, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "400",
    color: "rgba(87,87,87,1)",
    textAlign: "right",
    justifyContent: "flex-end",
  },

  Button: {
    display: "flex",
    flexDirection: "column",
    justifyContent: "center",
    alignItems: "center",
    paddingTop: 15,
    paddingBottom: 15,
    paddingLeft: 23,
    paddingRight: 23,
    borderRadius: 4,
    borderWidth: 1,
    borderStyle: "solid",
    borderColor: "rgba(253,169,42,1)",
    width: 388,
  },
  Login: {
    fontSize: 20,
    fontFamily: "Urbanist, sans-serif",
    fontWeight: "700",
    letterSpacing: -0.4,
    color: "rgba(253,169,42,1)",
    textAlign: "center",
    justifyContent: "center",
    textTransform: "uppercase",
  },

  reg: {
    main: "Txt2410",
    seg1: "[object Object]",
    seg2: "[object Object]",
  },
});
